{"tid":148151,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"iTunes 問題","createTime":"2017-03-08T11:21:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-11T09:26:36.000Z","uid":76449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7671138fe948731598092b1bfe1f4dfde1a407a0","tid":148151,"uid":76449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:21:21.000Z","msg":"已重新安裝好幾次<br />\n系統版本: win 7 64<br />\n<br />\n當連接iPhone之後, iTunes顯示 <br />\n&quot;無法使用此iPhone, 因為未安裝所需的軟體。請執行安裝程式來移除iTunes, 然後重新安裝iTunes。&quot;<br />\n試過各種重裝/用佢個安裝程式黎修復都係無用, 然後有再google過<br />\n<br />\n1. 跟呢條link去搵AMDS, services.msc 入面完全無 Apple Mobile Device: <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/HT203188?&amp;cid=acs::fm-itunes_HT203188-307078\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fzh-tw%2FHT203188%3F%26cid%3Dacs%3A%3Afm-itunes_HT203188-307078&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1P7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=aede4217\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/HT203188?&amp;cid=acs::fm-itunes_HT203188-307078</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 跟呢條link去做, 係可攜式裝置入面有見到&quot;Apple iPhone&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/HT204095\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fzh-tw%2FHT204095&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1P7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=b4608860\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/HT204095</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 再跟呢條link去更新, 去到7. 揀完之後彈出<br />\n&quot;你指定的資料夾沒有包含裝置可使用的相容軟貉驅動程式。如果資料夾中含有驅動程式, 請確認它已設計為搭配 適用於x64型系統的windows使用。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n然後我宜家就企左係度, 搵唔到任何可以做既野, 請求各位巴絲幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f68bf6ed95a4292e2bfca5845bb586ffc918be89","tid":148151,"uid":76449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji